\n| align=center| 3\u20130\n| [[Caol Uno]]\n| KO (punches)\n| [[UFC 34]]\n| {{dts|2001|November|2|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 0:11\n| [[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n| {{small|[[List of UFC Champions#Lightweight Championship|UFC Lightweight]] title eliminator.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 2\u20130\n| [[Din Thomas]]\n| KO (knee and punches)\n| [[UFC 32]]\n| {{dts|2001|June|29|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2:42\n| [[East Rutherford, New Jersey]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 1\u20130\n| Joey Gilbert\n| TKO (punches)\n| [[UFC 31]]\n| {{dts|2001|May|4|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 4:57\n| [[Atlantic City, New Jersey]], United States\n| \n{{end}}\n<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sherdog.com/fighter/BJ-Penn-1307|title=B.J.|last=Sherdog.com|website=Sherdog|access-date=2018-12-30}}</ref>\n\n==Pay-per-view bouts==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!No.\n!Event\n!Fight\n!Date\n!PPV Buys\n|-\n|1.\n|[[UFC 63]]\n|'''Hughes''' vs. '''Penn'''\n|September 23, 2006\n|400,000\n|-\n|2.\n|[[UFC 80]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Stevenson'''\n|January 19, 2008\n|225,000\n|-\n|3.\n|[[UFC 84]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Sherk'''\n|May 24, 2008\n|475,000\n|-\n|4.\n|[[UFC 94]]\n|'''St-Pierre''' vs. '''Penn 2'''\n|January 31, 2009\n|920,000\n|-\n|5.\n|[[UFC 101]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Florian'''\n|August 8, 2009\n|850,000\n|-\n|6.\n|[[UFC 107]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Sanchez'''\n|December 12, 2009\n|620,000\n|-\n|7.\n|[[UFC 112]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Edgar''' (co)\n|April 10, 2010\n|500,000\n|-\n|8.\n|[[UFC 118]]\n|'''Edgar''' vs. '''Penn 2'''\n|August 28, 2010\n|570,000\n|-\n|9.\n|[[UFC 123]]\n|'''Hughes''' vs. '''Penn''' (co)\n|November 20, 2010\n|500,000\n|-\n|10.\n|[[UFC 127]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Fitch'''\n|February 27, 2011\n|260,000\n|-\n|11.\n|[[UFC 137]]\n|'''Penn''' vs. '''Diaz'''\n|October 29, 2011\n|280,000\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |Total sales\n!5,600,000\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Film and television===\n{|