.asp?aid=455&issid=33 |archivedate=July 11, 2011 |df=mdy }}</ref>\n{{Col-2}}\n\n*'''[[Bleacher Report]]'''\n**2000s Lightweight Fighter of the Decade<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/313619-mma-awards-of-the-decade/page/11 |title=MMA Awards of the Decade |date=December 23, 2009}}</ref>\n**MMA's Greatest Lightweight of All-time<ref name=\"ReferenceA\"/><ref name=\"bleacherreport.com\"/><ref name=\"http\"/><ref name=\"ReferenceB\"/>\n*'''[[Black Belt Magazine]]'''\n**[[Black Belt Magazine]] Hall of Fame<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.blackbeltmag.com/daily/martial-arts-videos/mma-videos/bj-penn-blackbelt-hall-of-fame/ |title=BJ PENN INDUCTED INTO THE BLACKBELT HALL OF FAME |publisher=BlackBeltMag.com |last=Horwitz |first=Raymond}}</ref>\n**NHB Fighter of the Year (2008)\n*'''[[Eurosport Fight Club]]'''\n**[[Contact sport#Full-contact|Full-Contact]] Fighter of the Year (2004)<ref name=\"Pusey\">{{cite news|last=Pusey|first=Trent|title=2008 Inside Fights Awards|url=http://eurosport.com/2007/01/05/63762/|accessdate=September 5, 2012|publisher=Eurosport|date=January 5, 2007}}{{dead link|date=December 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n**Fight of the Year (2006) <small>vs. [[Matt Hughes (fighter)|Matt Hughes]] on September 23, 2006</small><ref name=\"Pusey\"/>\n*'''[[Sherdog|Sherdog Awards]]'''\n**Mixed Martial Arts Hall of Fame<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sherdog.com/news/articles/11/Imagining-an-MMA-Hall-of-Fame-The-ShooIns-71497 |title=SHERDOG.COM'S MMA HALL OF FAME |publisher=Sherdog.com |last=Martin |first=Todd}}</ref>\n**[[Sherdog#Fighter of the Year|Fighter of the Year \u2013 Honorable Mention]] (2004)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sherdog.com/news/news/Sherdogcom-Names-Wanderlei-Silva-2004-Fighter-of-the-Year-2259|title=Sherdog.com Names Wanderlei Silva 2004 Fighter of the Year|first=|last=Sherdog.com|publisher=}}</ref>\n**[[Sherdog#Beatdown of the Year|Beatdown of the Year (2008)]] <small>vs. [[Joe Stevenson]] on January 19, 2008</small><ref>[http://www.sherdog.com/news/articles/7/Sherdogs-Miscellaneous-Awards-for-2008-15727 Beatdown of the Year \u2013 Sherdog\u2019s Miscellaneous Awards for 2008]. Sherdog.com. Retrieved on October 30, 2011.</ref>\n\n===Submission grappling===\n*'''[[International Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu Federation|IBJJF World Championships]]'''\n**2000 \u2013 [[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship#Feather .28Pena.29|Black Belt Pena: 1st Place]]\n**1999 \u2013 [[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship#Light .28Leve.29|Brown Belt Leve: 3rd Place]]\n**1998 \u2013 [[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship#Feather .28Pena.29|Blue Belt Pena: 2nd Place]]\n**CBJJ Brazilian Team Championships\n**2000 \u2013 Marrom Preta Leve: [[Nova Uni\u00e3o (mixed martial arts)|Nova Uniao]], 1st Place\n*'''Other Credentials'''\n**[[Grapplers Quest]] Lightweight Championship Superfight Winner\n**1997 [[Joe Moreira]] Tournament \u2013 [[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Blue belt|Blue belt]], 1st place\n**1999 Copa Pacific Tournament \u2013 Gold medal\n**[[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Black belt|Black belt]] awarded 3 weeks prior to the 2000 World Jiu-Jitsu Championship\n**Believed to have earned the fastest [[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Black belt|Black belt]] of all Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu practitioners\n\n===Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu===\n*'''[[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship]]'''\n** [[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship|World Jiu-Jitsu Championship Gold Medal]]; [[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Black belt|Black belt]] division\n** [[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship|World Jiu-Jitsu Championship Silver Medal]]; [[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Blue belt|Blue belt]] division\n** [[World Jiu-Jitsu Championship|World Jiu-Jitsu Championship Bronze Medal]]; [[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Brown belt|Brown belt]] division\n**First American to win gold in the [[Brazilian jiu-jitsu ranking system#Black belt|Black belt]] category\n*'''Awards'''\n**[[Nova Uni\u00e3o (mixed martial arts)|Nova Uni\u00e3o Competition Team]] (