r |first2=Frederick H. |title=Prophet in Politics: Henry A. Wallace and the War Years, 1940\u20131965 |date=1970 |publisher=Iowa University Press |isbn=9780813812953|url=https://archive.org/details/henryawallaceofi00scha}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Schmidt |first1=Karl M. |title=Henry A. Wallace, Quixotic Crusade 1948 |url=https://archive.org/details/henryawallacequi00schm |date=1960 |publisher=Syracuse University Press |isbn=0815600208}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Walker |first1=J. Samuel |title=Henry A. Wallace and American Foreign Policy |date=1976 |publisher=Greenwood Press |isbn=9780837187747}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Witcover |first1=Jules |title=The American Vice Presidency: From Irrelevance to Power |date=2014 |publisher=Smithsonian Institution |isbn=9781588344724}}\n{{refend}}\n\n===Works by Wallace===\n{{refbegin|2}}\n* ''Agricultural Prices '' (1920)\n* ''New Frontiers '' (1934)\n* ''America Must Choose '' (1934)\n* ''Statesmanship and Religion '' (1934)\n* ''Technology, Corporations, and the General Welfare '' (1937)\n* ''The Century of the Common Man '' (1943)\n* ''Democracy Reborn '' (1944)\n* ''Sixty Million Jobs '' (1945)\n* ''Soviet Asia Mission '' (1946)\n* ''Toward World Peace '' (1948)\n* ''Where I Was Wrong '' (1952)\n* ''The Price of Vision \u2013 The Diary of Henry A. Wallace 1942\u20131946'' (1973), edited by John Morton Blum\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Henry Wallace}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\n* {{CongBio|W000077|ref=none}}\n* [http://wgf.org/ The Wallace Global Fund]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20071206031445/http://newdeal.feri.org/wallace/docs.htm Selected Works of Henry A. Wallace]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070929124714/http://www.winrock.org/wallace/wallacecenter/wallace/CCM.htm The text of Wallace's 1942 speech \"The Century of the Common Man\"]\n* [http://americanrhetoric.com/speeches/henrywallacefreeworldassoc.htm As delivered transcript and complete audio of Wallace's 1942 \"The Century of the Common Man\" Address]\